reviewText: I find this show very educational in a very friendly way. My infant laughs and is totally absorbed by it.We have watched it ten times now, along with the other shows we have: Club House, New Friends, Music, etc.It is a great show for kids. It teaches first of all that the essence of someone's character is in their heart, not their looks.I recommend it.
summary: Another Wonderful Yo Gabba Gabba show!
Title: Yo Gabba Gabba!: Birthday Boogie

reviewText: Yo Gabba Gabba teaches kids many good qualities...how to share.....care for others....behave in a group.....eating healthy.....all the things children need to learn to become productive and caring adults. My infant granddaughter is still too young to comprehend the messages. but for now she will settle for the lively music and entertaining, colorful characters.
Title: Yo Gabba Gabba!: Birthday Boogie

reviewText: My granddaughter love Yo Gabba Gabba so buying this dvd was worth it. I recommend this dvd to all parents.
Title: Yo Gabba Gabba!: Birthday Boogie

reviewText: Our son loves his Yo Gabba Gabba and I love that we can get these DVDs at such a cheap price.
